1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@| ><Routines$Dir>.!Boot
| Copyright © 2008, 7th software
| All rights reserved.

Set Routines$Dir     <Obey$Dir>
Set Routines$Path    <Routines$Dir>.Routines.
Set Routines$Linker  <Routines$Dir>.Resources.Linker
Set RoutinesRes$Path <Routines$Dir>.Resources.UK.,<Routines$Dir>.Resources.
Run RoutinesRes:LocaleRes Tmp$Locale
If "<Tmp$Locale>" <> "UK" Then Set RoutinesRes$Path <Routines$Dir>.Resources.<Tmp$Locale>.,<RoutinesRes$Path>
Unset Tmp$Locale
Set RoutinesMods$Path RoutinesRes:RM.
IconSprites <Routines$Dir>.!Sprites
@


1.1.1.1
log
@Imported some tools which are useful for builds.

* UnTarBZ2
* CreateSEC
* Routines

Various bits of software which are useful for building stuff should really
live in the RISC OS source tree somewhere. !Routines is a special case; it's
required by !CreateSEC and the source code to all its various bits lives at
7th software, but putting a binary import in RiscOS/Apps isn't that unusual.
@
text
@@
